sent=[]
label=[]
for i in c:
    i=i.split("\t")
    if len(i)==2:
        sent.append(i[0])
        label.append(int(i[1]))

from tensorflow.keras import Input
from tensorflow.keras import Model
In [52]:
inputs=Input(shape=(features,))
x1=Embedding(input_dim=vocal_len+1,output_dim=32,\
            input_length=features,
            embeddings_regularizer=keras.regularizers.l2(.001))(inputs)
x1=LSTM(100,dropout=0.3,recurrent_dropout=0.2)(x1)
outputs=Dense(1,activation="sigmoid")(x1)
model=Model(inputs,outputs)

In [59]:
def build(self,input_shape):
    self.W=self.add_weight(name="att_weight",shape=(input_shape[-1],1),initializer="normal")
    self.b=self.add_weight(name="att_bias",shape=(input_shape[1],1),initializer="zeros")
    super(attention,self).build(input_shape)
In [73]:
def cal(self,x):
    et=K.sequeeze(K.tanh(K.dot(x,self.W)+self.b),axis=-1)
    at=K.softmax(et)
    at=K.expand_dims(at,axis=-1)
    output=x*at
    return K.sum(output,axis=1)
In [67]:
from keras.layers import Layer
import keras.backend as K
In [76]:
class attention(Layer):
    def __init__(self,**kwargs):
        super(attention,self).__init__(**kwargs)

    def build(self,input_shape):
        self.W=self.add_weight(name="att_weight",shape=(input_shape[-1],1),initializer="normal")
        self.b=self.add_weight(name="att_bias",shape=(input_shape[1],1),initializer="zeros")        
        super(attention, self).build(input_shape)

    def call(self,x):
        et=K.squeeze(K.tanh(K.dot(x,self.W)+self.b),axis=-1)
        at=K.softmax(et)
        at=K.expand_dims(at,axis=-1)
        output=x*at
        return K.sum(output,axis=1)
        
    def compute_output_shape(self,input_shape):
        return (input_shape[0],input_shape[-1])

    def get_config(self):
        return super(attention,self).get_config()
In [77]:
inputs1=Input((features))
x=Embedding(input_dim=vocal_len+1,output_dim=32,input_length=features,\
            embeddings_regularizer=keras.regularizers.l2(.001))(inputs1)
att_in=LSTM(100,return_sequences=True,dropout=0.3,recurrent_dropout=0.2)(x)
att_out=attention()(att_in)
outputs1=Dense(1,activation='sigmoid',trainable=True)(att_out)
model1=Model(inputs1,outputs1)
